    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "track1_text",
      "x": 30,
      "y": 168,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 226,
      "text": "Track 1 — Architecture Document\n(structural sections)\n\n* System context & boundaries\n* Major components\n* Logical data flow\n* Security / auth model sketch\n* Deployment topology\n\n[Open: Claude patterns, Sheets\nmodel, Slack UX, mobile]",
